query:
/*+  */ select acc.location,
count(*)
from site AS s
inner join tag AS t1
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('drupal',
'electronics',
'math') AND t1.name IN ('binomial-theorem',
'convolution',
'covering-spaces',
'infinite-product',
'laurent-series',
'uniform-continuity')
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND t1.id = tq1.tag_id
inner join question AS q1
on s.site_id = q1.site_id AND q1.id = a1.question_id AND q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.score >= 0 AND q1.score <= 1000
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.downvotes >= 0 AND u1.downvotes <= 1
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND b.name IN ('Announcer',
'Constituent',
'Enlightened',
'Excavator',
'Explainer',
'Fanatic',
'Good Answer',
'Inquisitive',
'Self-Learner',
'Suffrage')
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id group by acc.location order by count(*) desc LIMIT 100;
